import React from 'react';
import { ThemeProvider, createTheme } from '@mui/material/styles';
import CssBaseline from '@mui/material/CssBaseline';
import { 
  Box, 
  Container, 
  Grid, 
  Paper, 
  Typography, 
  Card, 
  CardContent,
  Avatar,
  Divider,
  LinearProgress,
  Chip
} from '@mui/material';
import TrendingDownIcon from '@mui/icons-material/TrendingDown';
import TrendingUpIcon from '@mui/icons-material/TrendingUp';
import WarningIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Warning';
import StorageIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Storage';
import CloudIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Cloud';
import SpeedIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Speed';
import CheckCircleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CheckCircle';

// Dados mockados expandidos
const mockData = {
  metrics: {
    energyConsumption: {
      current: 1500,
      previous: 1800,
      reduction: 16.7,
      unit: "kWh",
      icon: <SpeedIcon />,
      color: "#4caf50"
    },
    digitalStorage: {
      current: 500,
      previous: 700,
      reduction: 28.6,
      unit: "GB",
      icon: <StorageIcon />,
      color: "#2196f3"
    },
    carbonEmissions: {
      current: 200,
      previous: 250,
      reduction: 20,
      unit: "kg CO2",
      icon: <CloudIcon />,
      color: "#f44336"
    }
  },
  suggestions: [
    {
      id: 1,
      title: "Otimizar Armazenamento em Nuvem",
      description: "Identificamos 200GB de arquivos duplicados que podem ser removidos",
      impact: "Redução de 15% no consumo de energia",
      priority: "high",
      progress: 75,
      status: "Em andamento"
    },
    {
      id: 2,
      title: "Ajustar Configurações de Servidores",
      description: "Configurar hibernação automática em períodos de baixa atividade",
      impact: "Redução de 10% no consumo de energia",
      priority: "medium",
      progress: 30,
      status: "Planejado"
    },
    {
      id: 3,
      title: "Implementar Virtualização",
      description: "Consolidar servidores físicos em máquinas virtuais",
      impact: "Redução de 25% no consumo de energia",
      priority: "high",
      progress: 10,
      status: "Planejado"
    }
  ],
  achievements: [
    {
      title: "Certificação Green IT",
      description: "Conquistada em 2023",
      icon: <CheckCircleIcon />
    },
    {
      title: "Redução de 20% em Emissões",
      description: "Meta atingida em 6 meses",
      icon: <SpeedIcon />
    }
  ]
};

const theme = createTheme({
  palette: {
    primary: {
      main: '#2e7d32',
    },
    secondary: {
      main: '#81c784',
    },
    background: {
      default: '#f5f5f5',
    },
  },
});

function App() {
  return (
    <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
      <CssBaseline />
      <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1, minHeight: '100vh', p: 3, bgcolor: 'background.default' }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg">
          {/* Header */}
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 4 }}>
            <Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: 'primary.main', mr: 2 }}>
              <CheckCircleIcon />
            </Avatar>
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" color="primary.main">
                EcoBot Dashboard
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary">
                Monitoramento de Sustentabilidade e ESG
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Box>
          
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            {/* Métricas */}
            <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
              <Paper sx={{ p: 3, height: '100%' }}>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                  <SpeedIcon sx={{ mr: 1 }} />
                  Métricas de Sustentabilidade
                </Typography>
                <Grid container spacing={2}>
                  {Object.entries(mockData.metrics).map(([key, value]) => (
                    <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={key}>
                      <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
                        <CardContent>
                          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                            <Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: value.color, mr: 2 }}>
                              {value.icon}
                            </Avatar>
                            <Typography variant="h6" component="div">
                              {key.replace(/([A-Z])/g, ' $1').replace(/^./, str => str.toUpperCase())}
                            </Typography>
                          </Box>
                          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 1 }}>
                            <Typography variant="h4" component="div" sx={{ mr: 1 }}>
                              {value.current}
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                              {value.unit}
                            </Typography>
                          </Box>
                          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', color: value.reduction > 0 ? 'success.main' : 'error.main' }}>
                              {value.reduction > 0 ? <TrendingDownIcon /> : <TrendingUpIcon />}
                              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ ml: 0.5 }}>
                                {Math.abs(value.reduction)}%
                              </Typography>
                            </Box>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ ml: 2 }}>
                              vs. anterior: {value.previous} {value.unit}
                            </Typography>
                          </Box>
                          <LinearProgress 
                            variant="determinate" 
                            value={value.reduction > 0 ? 100 : 0} 
                            color={value.reduction > 0 ? "success" : "error"}
                            sx={{ height: 8, borderRadius: 4 }}
                          />
                        </CardContent>
                      </Card>
                    </Grid>
                  ))}
                </Grid>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>

            {/* ChatBot e Conquistas */}
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
              <Grid container spacing={3}>
                {/* ChatBot */}
                <Grid item xs={12}>
                  <Paper sx={{ p: 3, height: '100%' }}>
                    <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                      <CheckCircleIcon sx={{ mr: 1 }} />
                      EcoBot Assistant
                    </Typography>
                    <Box sx={{ height: 200, overflow: 'auto', bgcolor: 'background.default', p: 2, borderRadius: 1, mb: 2 }}>
                      <Typography variant="body1" color="primary">
                        Olá! Como posso ajudar com sua gestão sustentável hoje?
                      </Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                        Digite "consumo" para ver métricas de consumo
                      </Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2">
                        Digite "sugestões" para ver recomendações
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                    <Divider sx={{ my: 2 }} />
                    <Typography variant="subtitle2" color="text.secondary">
                      Dicas rápidas:
                    </Typography>
                    <Box sx={{ mt: 1 }}>
                      <Chip label="Verificar consumo atual" size="small" sx={{ mr: 1, mb: 1 }} />
                      <Chip label="Sugestões de economia" size="small" sx={{ mr: 1, mb: 1 }} />
                      <Chip label="Relatórios ESG" size="small" sx={{ mb: 1 }} />
                    </Box>
                  </Paper>
                </Grid>

                {/* Conquistas */}
                <Grid item xs={12}>
                  <Paper sx={{ p: 3 }}>
                    <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                      <CheckCircleIcon sx={{ mr: 1 }} />
                      Conquistas
                    </Typography>
                    {mockData.achievements.map((achievement, index) => (
                      <Box key={index} sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                        <Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: 'primary.main', mr: 2 }}>
                          {achievement.icon}
                        </Avatar>
                        <Box>
                          <Typography variant="subtitle1">{achievement.title}</Typography>
                          <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                            {achievement.description}
                          </Typography>
                        </Box>
                      </Box>
                    ))}
                  </Paper>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>

            {/* Sugestões */}
            <Grid item xs={12}>
              <Paper sx={{ p: 3 }}>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                  <CheckCircleIcon sx={{ mr: 1 }} />
                  Sugestões de Melhoria
                </Typography>
                <Grid container spacing={2}>
                  {mockData.suggestions.map((suggestion) => (
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={4} key={suggestion.id}>
                      <Paper
                        sx={{
                          p: 2,
                          height: '100%',
                          bgcolor: 'background.paper',
                          border: 1,
                          borderColor: 'divider',
                        }}
                      >
                        <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 1 }}>
                          <Typography variant="h6" color={suggestion.priority === 'high' ? 'error.main' : 'warning.main'}>
                            {suggestion.title}
                          </Typography>
                          <Chip 
                            label={suggestion.status} 
                            size="small" 
                            color={suggestion.status === 'Em andamento' ? 'primary' : 'default'}
                          />
                        </Box>
                        <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                          {suggestion.description}
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="success.main" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                          Impacto: {suggestion.impact}
                        </Typography>
                        <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 1 }}>
                          <Box sx={{ width: '100%', mr: 1 }}>
                            <LinearProgress 
                              variant="determinate" 
                              value={suggestion.progress} 
                              color={suggestion.priority === 'high' ? 'error' : 'warning'}
                            />
                          </Box>
                          <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                            {suggestion.progress}%
                          </Typography>
                        </Box>
                      </Paper>
                    </Grid>
                  ))}
                </Grid>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>
    </ThemeProvider>
  );
}

export default App;
